Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma Shu has obtained the Void Genome and recovered his powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has also materialized his own Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know? You don’t mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are things, Mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s cramped in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl’s pretty stubborn for a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But soon, all of this will be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can have lots of fun together…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…Triton.
