Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Yahiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu was pretty amazing, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t you going to say anything to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s a message from Ward 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai’s talking! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, there have been 34 invasion attempts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and 42,000 hacking attempts on Ward 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I have come to a conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I shall grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve decided to let this world determine each of your individual worths.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On December 25th, the current world shall end…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…and a new world shall begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kuhouin instructed me to use all his assets and connections to fight Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To do that, we’ll join forces with a PMC tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, a private military company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma Shu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would you fight with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll ask the rest of you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please lend us your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would someone tell me something first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s Gai trying to do exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fourth Apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai intends to cause Lost Christmas on a worldwide scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shibungi! No way, are you a ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m quite alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu. Gai gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Ouma Kurosu’s diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad’s?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have the right to die knowing everything…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…and the obligation as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Ouma Kurosu’s former best friend, isn’t that what you want, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}”Best friend…” There was a time when I could call him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was back when I was still a graduate student at Tennozu College.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:05:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the time, other people were nothing but annoyances to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keido! This paper of yours is just too beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stop crying, I’m so moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I found out something when Ouma Kurosu appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There were others who could operate from the same conceptual framework as me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}argue theory with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and compete with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then the Genomic Resonance Theory Kurosu constructed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}on the basis of my Intron RAM Hypothesis
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}commanded worldwide attention as the key to unlocking the mysteries
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}of evolution and natural selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosu, look! Your paper is—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saeko Shijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A woman from the college’s medical school who was famous across campus for her accomplishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was already carrying Kurosu’s child by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before long, they were married
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and moved to Oshima, where her family lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Five years later…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check this out, Shuuichirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amino acid bonding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is… a Genomic Resonance reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Mana who found the meteorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll have to thank her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. This {\i1}is{\i0} a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Generally it’s not very infectious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, when it’s activated by Genomic Resonance…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It inserts itself into introns and starts replicating,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,causing structural sclerosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An instrument for playing the notes of Genomic Resonance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a trumpet for the Apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her growth is coming along nicely, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Yu. I’m an envoy of Daath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Daath”?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The meteorite has sown the seeds of Apocalypse across the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very soon, all the people of your country will become their seedbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Mana eventually matures as Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Earth will witness its fourth Apocalypse…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The simultaneous selection and evolution of all life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Apocalypse is the “invisible hand of God” at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosu, I believe your wife is symptomatic already,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you mustn’t kill her unborn child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eve appears intent on making him her Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, Ouma Shu was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the cost of his mother’s life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Adam that Eve desired…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unless something was done,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}both of Kurosu’s children would be responsible for our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His blood would set the standard of the next generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I thought of that, something inside me cracked. {KOOKOO}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosu turned me down…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what will you do, Shuuichirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s hear what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illegal immigration?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps they were kidnapped and intended to be sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the only one alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you’re awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m the man…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…who will be your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The place Keido brought me to was a facility
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}where he was rearing many male children,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}trying to create Adam,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a mate for Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You could call it a nursery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Experiment after experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were administered artificially strengthened Apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then I…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,”Triton.”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came from sea, so you’re Triton.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that a great name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ironic, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trying to escape one fate that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wound up trapped in an even bigger fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn’t that right, Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been a long time, hasn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, I didn’t notice you…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one of the student researchers? It’s nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve gotten you blankets before,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I’ve found you asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Keido Shuuichirou’s little sister, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude of me!
