Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had just skipped a grade and started college.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a smart aleck who lived too much in her head,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kurosu triggered my curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He left his children behind in Oshima
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to immerse himself in his research, forgetting to eat and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To me, he looked like a martyr fighting the virus in solitude.
